        "func": "let d = msg.payload;\n// Hanya tambah ID & Waktu jika kosong (dari Wokwi)\nif (!d.id) {\n    d.id = \"WKW-GRD-\" + Date.now();\n    d.timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n}\nmsg.payload = d;\nreturn msg;",
